Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.91,0:00:58.07,OPCNchs,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}争相怒放！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.45,0:01:04.01,OPCNchs,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}为了搞懂 绞尽脑汁
